    "_comment": "CMS-in-CMS template: a Contact Directory in three pages — the compact list-only variant of the pattern (no public detail page). PUBLIC: /contacts renders a searchable-looking card grid with avatar initials, department badge and tap-to-call / tap-to-mail links. ADMIN (CMS surface): /cms/contacts is an entry-table CRUD grid and /cms/contacts/form is one create+edit form page with two routes (blank = create, /{record_id} = update) opened as a modal. Data binding is portable via \"@section:contacts-form\" tokens; data_tables[] carries columns + sample rows (import with options.importData=true). Content locales: de-CH + en-GB. Use a keyword + route prefix to import a second copy — in-content links are rewritten automatically. Import via Admin > Pages > Import. NOT auto-seeded.",
